The paper proposes a novel CTR model that leverages users' historical behavior sequences, which is a common topic in machine learning and information retrieval (cs.LG, cs.IR). The model uses self-attention mechanism, Bi-LSTM, and local activation unit, which are popular deep learning techniques in natural language processing and computer vision (cs.CL, cs.CV). The paper also mentions online advertising and recommender systems, which are common applications of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
